Interface AHOffer

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface AHOffer
extends AHOfferModel, com.liferay.portal.model.PersistedModel
    The extended model interface for the AHOffer service. Represents a row in the "AHOFFER" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.
    Author:
